summary:
Passionated and enthusiastic about getting the best out of people and teams with a continuous drive to learn, improve and let the business grow with customer excellence as highest priority. Recognized as genuine, open-minded person and operating with vision, focus and strong bias to action. 

Goal:
Bring added value to customers, the company I work for and the ecosystem I be member of. 

Result-driven, adaptable and high energy senior sales professional with 22+ years of B2B commercial experience. Trademark in creating, innovating new business and building & mastering successful strategic relationships with clients and partners. Operated in different domestic and international sales leadership positions in EMEA. 

Specialties: 
Leadership – Sales - Adaptable - Empathic - Determined - Entrepreneurial – Networker. 
Result driven - Team Player - Creative - Pro-active - Customer focused and oriented.
